      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "All records for rapid real estate\nselling in Spokane have been\nbroken by Messrs. Francis and\nRhoades with their addition, Spo-\nkane Terrace.\n\n\nThis addition went on sale, as adj\nvertised in Saturdays Press, yes\nterday morning, and upto 9:15 this\nmorning 5S7 lots had been sold\nThe dealers expect to close out the\nentire addition in less than 1C\ndays.\n\n\nThe gentlemen lately came here\nfrom Missoula, and this is their\nfirst venture in Spokane real\nestate. They are dong business on\nthe 81 down and 81 week pay\nment plan."
    }
